    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The Foam Roller for Myofasical Release Poster provides detailed exercises to assist in soft tissue therapy for the treatment of skeletal muscle pain. Myofasical release exercise help to work muscles, improve blood and lymphatic circulation, and improve stretching. Moreover this chart offers the tips you need to improve your health and your exercise performance. This brilliant full-color 24”x36” laminated poster by Productive Fitness Publishing will look great on your wall.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Productive Fitness Home Gym Work Out Poster - Laminated (Many Exercises)</h2>\n  <p>The Foam Roller for Myofasical Release Poster provides detailed exercises to assist in soft tissue therapy for the treatment of skeletal muscle pain. Myofasical release exercise help to work muscles, improve blood and lymphatic circulation, and improve stretching. Moreover this chart offers the tips you need to improve your health and your exercise performance.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>Dimensions:</strong> 24&quot; x 36&quot;</li>\n    <li>Laminated</li>\n    <li>Written &amp; Designed by Fitness Experts</li>\n    <li>Intended to Teach Proper Exercise Technique &amp; Form</li>\n    <li>Detailed w/ Easy To Follow Step by Step 